descriptionHtml:
Music Player is an offline music player for android and provides powerful music play functionality, after call ringtone menu and the best user interface. Even customize your call ringtones to each contact in your phone book!

Features:
• Play music quickly and easily
• Listen to your favorite music with this powerful equalizer
• Set ringtones for contacts in phone book
• Easy change and set new ringtones after calls.
• Supports playback of various sound formats such as MP3, AAC, FLAC
• Manage song lists by categories: Album, Artist, Genre, Folder, Playlists
• Offline music player, songs player, audio player, mp3 player with high quality
• Play music offline in shuffle, order, or loop
• Stay on top of your schedule on calls with the calendar and notification menu
• Background music player and Sleep timer to turn off the player automatically
• Free music app with all controls

Music Player app is a digital music player that lets you play music and any media file on your android phone. Powerful music player is a free and unlimited Music app.

This music player app is a simple music player. Listen to all kinds of music with Default Music, a great music player that supports MP3, WMA, AAC, and FLAC files. Not only that, but this app will instantly detect, import, and organize all the music on your device. Music Player is a truly efficient audio player for Android.

Free Music Player has all the features you wish for in a great Android music player, including lock screen controls and the ability to create playlists. This app also has an equalizer you can use to customize the playback. Your library will automatically organize and separate the songs into albums and authors.

Overall, Mp3 Player is a great music player with a sleek interface and many features. Offline music is the default music player app for free to play your favorite music offline.
